product_ranges.title: The Ultimate French Press Guide Print

global-fap.description:
Resulting from the process of writing the World Atlas of Coffee, this poster shows a selection of the most common coffee varieties, and how they connect to each other as well as when they came to be.

Giclée printed on premium quality heavyweight 200gsm fine art A1 paper. 

Printed on demand - please allow 10-15 business days for delivery (ships from AU, NL & US)

Bryan Schiele (@letsbrew.coffee)
